    <stitle>INSTRUMENTS - TACHOMETER - HOURMETER (OPTIONAL)</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="0">
        <title>HOURMETER (OPTIONAL)</title>
        <para>The hourmeter is a solenoid activated mechanical counter type unit driven by the microprocessor. The
            microprocessor internal timer advances the hourmeter 1/10 hour for every 6 minutes that the engine is above
            300 rpm. In addition, the microprocessor internal timer advances 3 minutes every time the ignition is turned
            on to minimize hourmeter error. This provides for a very accurate engine hourmeter.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
